Class LoggerModel

java.lang.Object
org.supsi.model.info.LoggerModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
BasicLogModel, ILoggerModel
public class LoggerModel extends Object implements ILoggerModel
Represents the logging model for managing log entries of various types. Allows adding logs based on their type and controlling the visibility of each log type.
